      MAINTAINER=nhudson@speakeasy.net
           SHORT="Ruby-GConf is bindings for Ruby to GConf"
cat << EOF
Ruby-GNOME is a set of Ruby language bindings for the GNOME development
environment. At the moment, the most mature of these is the Ruby-GTK
library, but bindings for libgnome, libgnomeui, gdk-pixbuf, gdk-imlib,
libglade, libpanel-applet and GConf are in various stages of
development.
EOF
